<h2>Dry skin and Vaginal dryness</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms dry skin and vaginal dryness including Sunburn, Wind exposure, and Perimenopause.</p>
<p>There  are 5 conditions  associated with dry skin and vaginal dryness. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
